{"lemma":"فِكْرُ","slug":"فِكْرُ","root":"ف.ك.ر","root_slug":"ف-ك-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-ك-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"فِكْرُ","root":"فكر","pos":"V","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":11},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["","n34385","n34386"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D9%90%D9%83%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to think, ponder over","tags":["uncommon"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to reflect, to meditate, to contemplate"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to think","examples":[{"text":"إِنَّهُۥ فَكَّرَ وَقَدَّرَ","english":"he contemplated and determined"},{"text":"لَوْ فَكَّرَ الْعَاشِقُ فِي مُنْتَهَى / حُسْنِ الَّذِي يَسْبِيهِ لَمْ يَسْبِهِ","english":"(please add an English translation of this quotation)"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to consider"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of فَكَرَ (fakara, “to think”) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"thinking"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"thinking"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"thought"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"thoughtful attention"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"idea","examples":[{"text":"لَا تَتَرَدَّدْ فِي مُشَارَكَةِ أَفْكَارِكَ.","english":"Don't hesitate to share your ideas."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of فِكْرَة (fikra)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Intensive of فَكَرَ (fakara, “to think”)."},"ipa":["/fa.ka.ra/","/fak.ka.ra/","/fakr/","/fikr/","/fi.kar/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n34385","headword_ar":"فَكْرٌ","root":"fkr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n. of 1 [q. v.]. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layosa liY fiY h`*aA AlA^amori","text_ar":"لَيْسَ لِى فِى هٰذَا الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fakorN","text_ar":"فَكْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Yaakoob, S, O, K, *) which is more chaste than ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fikorN","text_ar":"فِكْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [in this case,] (Yaakoob, S, O,) but the latter is sometimes used, (K,) means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have no want,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"need, of this thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Yaakoob, S, O, K: *) or, as is said in the A,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA fakora liY fiY h`*aA","text_ar":"لَا فَكْرَ لِى فِى هٰذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have no want,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"need, of this, nor do I care for it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K"]},{"entry_id":"n34386","headword_ar":"فِكْرٌ","root":"fkr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fikorapN","text_ar":"فِكْرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fikoraY","text_ar":"فِكْرَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lth, O, K,) are simple substs., (S, O, Msb, *) but the last is of rare occurrence, (Lth, O,) signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thought, consideration,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mental"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"examination,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY A^amorK","text_ar":"فِى اَمْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"respecting a thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"consideration"},{"kind":"text","text":"[of a thing]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in order to obtain a clear knowledge"},{"kind":"text","text":"[of it]; (S, TA;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"employment of the mind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the consideration,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) upon a thing: (M, K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"repeated consideration for the purpose of seeking"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to discover"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"meanings:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arranging of things in the mind in order, by them, to arrive at some object of which the attainment is desired, though it be but a preponderating opinion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arranging of known things"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the mind"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in order to attain to"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the knowledge of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an unknown"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (KT:) pl. of the first"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afokaArN","text_ar":"اَفْكَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (IDrd, K;) but Sb says that neither"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fikorN","text_ar":"فِكْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"nor"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EilomN","text_ar":"عِلْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"nor"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naZarN","text_ar":"نَظَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"has any pl.: (TA:) the pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fikorapN","text_ar":"فِكْرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fikarN","text_ar":"فِكَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lifulaAnK fikarN kul~uhaA fiqarN","text_ar":"لِفُلَانٍ فِكَرٌ كُلُّهَا فِقَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one has thoughts all of which are points of wit"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fakorN","text_ar":"فَكْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","O","Msb","K","Lth","M","TA","KT"]}]}}